 your trace strength exceeded the Runner\'s link strength.','Play only if the Runner accessed a card during their last turn. Trace[4]. If successful, trash 1 installed program with an install cost of X or less, where X is equal to the amount by which your trace strength exceeded the Runner\'s link strength.',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,3,NULL,'Fei F. Ou',NULL,NULL,NULL,59,3,NULL,NULL,0,3,NULL),(519,14,2,8,1,'2026-03-18 10:22:33','2026-03-18 10:22:33','21060','TechnoCo','TechnoCo','Corporation','The install cost of each program, piece of hardware, and <strong>virtual</strong> resource is increased by 1.\nWhenever the Runner installs a program, piece of hardware, or <strong>virtual</strong> resource, you may gain 1[credit].','The install cost of each program, piece of hardware, and virtual resource is increased by 1. Whenever the Runner installs a program, piece of hardware, or virtual resource, you may gain 1 credit.',NULL,NULL,NULL,2,NULL,NULL,'Caravan Studio',NULL,NULL,NULL,60,3,NULL,2,1,3,NULL),(520,15,9,7,1,'2026-03-18 10:22:33','2026-03-18 10:22:33','09001','SYNC: Everything, Everywhere','SYNC: Everything, Everywhere','Division','[click]: Flip this identity.\nThe Runner pays 1[credit] more when spending a [click] to remove a tag (not through a card ability).\nFlip side:\n[click]: Flip this identity.\nYou may pay 2[credit] fewer when spending a [click] to trash a resource (not through a card ability).','click: Flip this identity. The Runner pays 1 credit more when spending a click to remove a tag (not through a card ability). Flip side: click: Flip this identity. You may pay 2 credits fewer when spending a click to trash a resource (not through a card ability).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Maciej Rebisz',15,NULL,40,1,3,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL),(521,15,9,7,1,'2026-03-18 10:22:33','2026-03-18 10:22:33','09002','New Angeles Sol: Your News','New Angeles Sol: Your News','Division','Whenever an agenda is scored or stolen, you may play 1 <strong>current</strong> from HQ or Archives 